      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 113,
      "message": "This might be beyond the scope of refactoring but where does the number 4 come form. It looks like a \"magic number\" to me.\nhttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Magic_number_(programming)\nI would prefer if this was at least a static constant with a meaningful name.",
