      "file_path": "PolicyEngineAPI/src/main/java/org/onap/policy/std/ManualClientEndDMAAP.java",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 118,
      "message": "I would suggest changing the return type of this method to a boolean indicating success or failure, and taking \"count\" out of it altogether.\n\nI would also suggest changing the name of \"cout\" to \"retries\" and changing the loop above to try calling the method up to RETRY_LIMIT times and then giving up on failure.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 2787,
        "name": "Liam Fallon",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "liam.fallon@est.tech",
        "username": "liamfallon"
      },
      "updated": "2018-07-26 11:03:09.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
