      "file_path": "PolicyEngineAPI/src/main/java/org/onap/policy/std/ManualClientEndDMAAP.java",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 126,
      "message": "This is bad practice because the statement \"count = 4\" is actually using a side effect of the logic. Really what we want to do here is \"return successfully, we are finished\".",
